patible with all versions.\n\n> If you want to use hardcore hearts without being in hardcore mode, use this [Real Hardcore Hearts](https://modrinth.com/project/fefCJvJI)\n\nI think you'll like it.\n\n[Sus](https://wplace.live/?lat=-12.156110924099828&lng=-41.66745150322268&zoom=16.040463277185847)\n\n  <p align=\"center\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/146981a830769d2a6661b1d49b33f4cfdf31f817.png\" alt=\"important!\" width=\"275\">\n    \n### *If you find any type of bug or error, report it on my [discord server!](https://discord.gg/CdHqyDxMrz)*",
